content:
Koodaaram mosha chamachappo-llellaarum
Kaazhchakallodetthi dhanavaanmaar po-nnarppichu
Vellllikkoottam kaazhchayanachu-aparanmaar
Pattaadakall chilar, vidhavasthree chilli-kkaasheki.
/tthalkkaaryam sabhaye kaanichu
/tthan sabhaye-nirmmichon Daivam
Svargatthilumee bhoomiyilum nithyam- sthuthyan thaan.
